OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778230885
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder jailed for eight
OL,4,Cyears for raping woman
OL,6,FThe co-founder of clothing firm
OL,7,FSuperdry has been jailed for eight
OL,8,Fyears after being convicted of raping
OL,9,Fa woman after a night out drinking.
OL,11,FJames Holder, 54, of Cheltenham,
OL,12,FGloucestershire, had gone back to the
OL,13,Fwoman's home, went to the toilet and
OL,14,Fthen promptly fell asleep on her bed
OL,15,Fsnoring.
OL,17,FHolder, a multimillionaire fashion
OL,18,Fboss, then woke up and beckoned the
OL,19,Fwoman, who was trying to sleep in her
OL,20,Flounge, into her bedroom and raped her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
