PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778230885
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder jailed for eight
OL,4,Cyears for raping woman
OL,6,FHe denied rape, claiming that the
OL,7,Fsexual activity had been consensual,
OL,8,Fbut was convicted by a jury at
OL,9,FCirencester Courthouse last week.
OL,11,FRecorder David Chidgey, sitting at
OL,12,FBristol Crown Court on Thursday,
OL,13,Fjailed Holder for eight years for the
OL,14,Foffence, describing it as "a
OL,15,Fdespicable piece of sexual violence".
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
