PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778230885
OL,3,CSuperdry co-founder jailed for eight
OL,4,Cyears for raping woman
OL,6,FThe judge said: "It was about
OL,7,Fentitlement, it was about your sense
OL,8,Fof entitlement and your sense of doing
OL,9,Fwhat you wanted and your causal
OL,10,Fdisregard for the victim's absolute
OL,11,Fright to say what she wanted to do
OL,12,Fwith her own body."
OL,14,FHolder, who appeared via video link
OL,15,Ffrom HMP Hewell wearing a grey
OL,16,Fsweatshirt and jogging bottoms, did
OL,17,Fnot react as the sentence was passed.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@SO]
